@startuml spec-lifecycle
title LiveSpec Core — Spec Lifecycle
skinparam defaultFontName Helvetica
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam BackgroundColor #fafafa
skinparam ArrowColor #000000
skinparam ArrowFontColor #000000
skinparam ArrowFontSize 11
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.3
skinparam nodesep 16
skinparam ranksep 26
hide stereotype

skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #d6e6f5
  BorderColor #1f4768
  FontColor #111
  RoundCorner 8
}
skinparam database {
  BackgroundColor #f5ead5
  BorderColor #5a4319
  FontColor #111
}
skinparam package {
  FontColor #111
  FontSize 13
  FontStyle bold
  BorderColor #444
  BorderThickness 2
}

rectangle "initial intent /\nprompt / instruction / seed" as Input #fffacc

package "SPEC SIDE" as SpecPkg #fde8ec {
  rectangle "/livespec:seed" as Seed
  rectangle "/livespec:propose-changes" as Propose
  rectangle "/livespec:critique" as Critique
  rectangle "/livespec:revise" as Revise
  rectangle "/livespec:doctor" as Doctor
  rectangle "/livespec:prune-history" as Prune

  database "SPECIFICATION/\n(spec.md, contracts.md,\nconstraints.md, scenarios.md,\nnon-functional-requirements.md)" as Spec #f5d76e
  database "proposed_changes/\n(pending)" as PCQueue
  database "history/vNNN/\n(snapshots +\nprocessed proposals)" as History
}

' Seed bootstraps spec + v001
Input --> Seed
Seed --> Spec : authors initial tree
Seed --> History : writes v001

' Direct authoring path
Propose --> PCQueue : writes pending\nproposed-change file

' Critique reads spec, emits findings as proposed changes
Spec --> Critique
Critique --> PCQueue : promotes findings\nto proposed changes

' Revise drains the queue, mutates spec, cuts new history snapshot
PCQueue --> Revise
Revise --> Spec : applies accepted\nresulting_files
Revise --> History : cuts new vNNN,\nrelocates processed\nproposals

' Doctor's pre/post-step invariants
Spec ..> Doctor : static + LLM-driven\ninvariants
PCQueue ..> Doctor : hygiene
History ..> Doctor : structural checks

' Prune collapses oldest history versions
History --> Prune
Prune --> History : pruned-marker

note right of Spec : Mutated ONLY through\n/livespec:propose-changes →\n/livespec:revise after the v001 seed.\nDirect edits forbidden.

note right of Revise : Selective per-proposal\naccept / modify / reject.\nEvery successful revise — including\nall-reject — cuts exactly one new\nvNNN, preserving the audit trail.

note bottom of PCQueue : Pure queue — drains via Revise.\nProcessed proposals relocate into\nhistory/vNNN/proposed_changes/ paired\nwith disposition revision files; they\ndo not accumulate here.

note bottom of History : Pure archive — items only enter\nvia Revise; never become pending,\nnever drain except via\n/livespec:prune-history.

@enduml
